title: Injustice - Gods Among Us - Year Two (001 - 024 + Annual) (2014)
description:
Injustice - Gods Among Us - Year Two (001 - 024 + Annual) (2014) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire) 


The digital release follow up to the hit Video Game Tie-In series Injustice: Gods Among Us by writer Tom Taylor. Unlike the previous volume which saw weekly digital release, Year Two moved to a bi-weekly schedule, with the print collection going from 30 pages to 20, and lowering a dollar in price AND only 24 issues in the second volume:(
